    "However, further exploration into why some respondents rated the bot less favorably could provide valuable insights.",
    "Most respondents acknowledged the bot's design as supportive of personalized learning; nonetheless, concerns were raised regarding potential overreliance on AI, which may hinder critical thinking skills.",
    "The students underscored that the interaction with the teacher and their peers cannot be usurped by anything else and provides certain benefits that might not be delivered online fully.",
    "To further explore students' responses to the statement \"POE is supposed to personalize learning,\" we inductively coded open-ended responses for 51 students into 14 themes, which are summarized in Table 6.",
    "The general response showed that the majority of students experienced the learning activity as interesting, helpful, and convenient for their learning processes."
